心咋！邊撚個搞到市民要搶口罩？政府呀！要屌屌政府啦。<br />\n<br />\n1.政府一早知疫情，仍毫無準備去確保口罩供應，所以大家先要搶。<br />\n<br />\n2.到口罩真係短缺，大家周圍去搶口罩，政府係呢件事上面仍然冇做過啲咩幫手(世界咁大，政府要搵口罩返黎會搵唔到？)由得香港人自生自滅，要天寒地凍起身排隊買一盒口罩。<br />\n<br />\n3.咁都算，喺市民搶口罩嘅同時，政府喺另一邊繼續開大個門俾帶菌嘅大陸人落黎播毒。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲你唔屌？你唔撚妥咪唔好撚排囉，返屋企坐定定等政府救你囉！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍絲、港豬 一定要大大力屌，特別係廢中廢老。<br />\n佢一屌啲職員你就可以開聲屌柒佢，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>係屌俾其他排緊隊嘅人聽</ins></span></strong>。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:19:53.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"4a0940429413ff9dea25d2660181c74872538668","tid":1851004,"uid":340189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:20:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔隔離內地人，任佢地出入，你日日都要落黎吹風呀！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6495adfded94fbc4c2c84a6f4e7814eafb242039","tid":1851004,"uid":102982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:20:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n齊齊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85860e9f27e1a4476da6b500096382f5ce9e722e","tid":1851004,"uid":108560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecaccec7c90d994651f3163fdcf0cea63377d8eb","tid":1851004,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:20:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b38f93b2d5626a6440da16bf4527abd6e1b721e","tid":1851004,"uid":281516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:21:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗疫保命<br />\n推翻暴政</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ca6a8489a7ed5e429a9c42d73c72812278d73448","tid":1851004,"uid":129202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01