一定係自己人扲哂！一定叫佢嘔反岀黎！<br />\n其實去到呢個地步我真係吾咁開門！呢班高層真係好冇人性！<br />\n亦好想借你呢到同大家講一講 去到呢個地步我地員工係冇辦法自己keep貨！因為不論咩時間反貨你地其實都係到望住開箱果下！<br />\n我地都靠公司每日比一個口罩我地<br />\n我夠膽講我地大部份員工之前都冇意識到呢個病令到口罩缺到咁！我地自己都冇買定存貨 我地都缺//<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n仆街啦，一定好多廢佬大媽屌，大家落定去差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"af5b4ffb3033af0b4044506a1a37dd6fa75572c7","tid":1851004,"uid":108560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8cc8c628fc60c523b95c0ebac9818c3c66e0ae","tid":1851004,"uid":147031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:53:21.000Z","msg":"要700萬人一齊屌政府先得"},{"pid":"29466bc04f536c8f1a4dfe76b76c4dc7f4e64833","tid":1851004,"uid":108560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fa68854ab81011bd722e730e6b20ae59092a9d","tid":1851004,"uid":20754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:55:29.000Z","msg":"手足加油😂"},{"pid":"25aa483baf0e8b06fc938c936f448978d1347c69","tid":1851004,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:56:51.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"c54a8e739d57da6043cb2020b7db4c4ea0a46205","tid":1851004,"uid":199254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"